<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>哈佛法律评论</title><link>https://harvardlawreview.org</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 14:03:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人身保护集体诉讼</title><link>https://harvardlawreview.org/print/vol-139/habeas-class-actions/</link><description>&lt;span class="post-card__excerpt"&gt;人身保护令案件可以作为集体诉讼进行吗？最高法院从未正面回答过这个问题，即使在下级法院认可人身保护令的案件中也是如此。但特朗普政府大规模驱逐非公民，迫使这个问题成为现代民权诉讼的中心。&lt;/span&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 21:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://harvardlawreview.org/print/vol-139/habeas-class-actions/</guid></item><item><title>王国的钥匙：移民控制和行政权力的增强</title><link>https://harvardlawreview.org/print/vol-139/keys-to-the-kingdom-immigration-control-and-the-accretion-of-executive-power/</link><description>&lt;span class="post-card__excerpt"&gt;在 2024 年总统竞选中，当时的候选人唐纳德·特朗普特别关注移民政策。与拜登政府的做法不同，特朗普承诺，如果他当选，他将对未经授权进入的移民“关闭边境”。&lt;/span&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 20:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://harvardlawreview.org/print/vol-139/keys-to-the-kingdom-immigration-control-and-the-accretion-of-executive-power/</guid></item></channel></rss>